HEADWORD: Rest cure
<hw>Rest cure</hw>. <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Treatment of severe nervous
disorder, as neurasthenia, by rest and isolation with systematic feeding
and the use of massage and electricity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

